app-publish - Publish applications

USAGE:
    app-publish

DESCRIPTION:
    Publish the current application to the app registry.
    Must be run from app directory.

CONFIGURATION:
    -conf-install-app-registry-git-url URL
        Git URL for app registry (default: https://github.com/walterjwhite/app.registry.git)

    -conf-install-app-registry-timeout SECONDS
        App registry timeout (default: 5)

EXAMPLES:
    app-publish
